column5: Vandals, accident or someone didn't want to pull it off/out of the ice anymore?  http://www.thebarrieexaminer.com/2015/02/20/ice-hut-goes-up-in-flames

Probably a propane refilling guy (just kidding).  Last winter a cottage buddy pulls his sweet, well insulated hut out, lights 1 burner of his 2 burner stove, locks the door and goes to town for minnows. KABOOOM!  I saw the aftermath, pretty scary.  Nobody hurt in either situation, that's a good thing.
Lucky for the owner they couldn't find the owner.  They might have had a bill to pay.
